TASK_SUBTASK_1_TITLE=W2.1: Standardize status file format on 'STATUS: BUSY' (colon+space). Update Go ctl.WriteStatus and any other Go writers under tui/cmd/doey-ctl/ to write the colon+space format. Verify all shell readers in .claude/hooks/ and shell/ work. Run tests/test-bash-compat.sh.
